csc171.project03.sprites

Class Spaceship

  • java.lang.Object
    • csc171.project03.sprites.AbstractSprite
      • csc171.project03.sprites.Spaceship

  • public class Spaceship
extends AbstractSprite
    This is the user controlled spaceship. It's a singleton because only one should exist per game.
